00:09:05.688 --> 00:09:08.154
Lungi dance, Lungi dance,
Lungi dance, Lungi dance,

00:09:08.154 --> 00:09:10.574
Lungi dance, Lungi dance,
Lungi dance, Lungi dance,

00:09:10.574 --> 00:09:13.244
Lungi dance, Lungi dance,
Lungi dance, Lungi -

